{"tid":633122,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華當年個廣告到咗而家真係害唔少Sales","createTime":"2018-04-18T04:31:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T06:48:06.000Z","uid":57632,"like":70,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5e476c84d1c8499b504fe01724c3c614f5260802","tid":633122,"uid":57632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:31:25.000Z","msg":"香港客閪並唔係一朝一夕嘅事<br />\n服務態度服務態度<br />\n我跪係地下推銷好冇？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說做左Sales半年<br />\n都差唔多明白點解其他同事成日屌香港人好閪<br />\n初頭以為大家開唔到單先屌<br />\n而家平均每兩至三日就有幾個閪客走黎<br />\n搞事嘅有，攞著數嘅又有<br />\n小弟做開電子產品銷售<br />\n周不時有啲客會走黎開你一啲商品問題<br />\n當然答你問題可以，但係可唔可以唔好咁撚串柒柒<br />\n仲要講撚到明話<br />\n&ldquo;買呢我就唔買㗎啦，不過你介紹黎俾我聽吓先&rdquo;<br />\n一旦講得唔夠詳細又開始屌你話<br />\n&ldquo;介紹到唔清唔楚咁，你係咪撈㗎&rdquo;<br />\n成日都開口埋口就<br />\n&ldquo;你呢啲咩服務態度啊？&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;我係客黎㗎&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;無我幫你開單，你下個月食屎啦&rdquo;<br />\n屌你老母臭閪Sales唔係人啊？<br />\n仆你個臭街你班閪客去含撚啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xR0jYg-9JBg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxR0jYg-9JBg&d=3BDfBKm6Na1HOiHBfCacPYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=6631d8d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xR0jYg-9JBg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DdgAZmL8ewo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDdgAZmL8ewo&d=3BDfBKm6Na1HOiHBfCacPYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=03e827c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DdgAZmL8ewo</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/q3_bjJ2MulE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fq3_bjJ2MulE&d=3BDfBKm6Na1HOiHBfCacPYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=afc6b86d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/q3_bjJ2MulE</a>"},{"pid":"c44bbc3e54fd633db6a70e83bfaae129b5ce9ff5","tid":633122,"uid":3558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:43:37.000Z","msg":"正評"},{"pid":"97c4ca70bc900a78989a877ca5c0cb147462c93d","tid":633122,"uid":23468,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:48:36.000Z","msg":"應該出返一套如何做客人嘅廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma